lead_paragraph: With GoDaddy set to end its sponsorship, the next few months will say a lot about Nascar’s health if Patrick, one of its most marketable drivers, has trouble landing a new corporate backer.

headline.print_headline: She’s Got Plenty of Fans. A New Sponsor? Not Yet.
headline.main: Danica Patrick Has Plenty of Fans. A New Sponsor? Not Yet.

snippet: With GoDaddy set to end its sponsorship, the next few months will say a lot about Nascar’s health if Patrick, one of its most marketable drivers, has trouble landing a new corporate backer.
abstract: Nascar driver Danica Patrick, one of auto racing's most marketable personalities, is looking for new sponsorship after end of partnership with GoDaddy; her ability to land a deal for next season will be bellwether for health of the sport.
